    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! It\u2019s been a fantastic, reliable ride for me, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep it in really solid shape. It runs great and is super clean\u2014perfect if you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home! Drop me a message if you have any questions or want to come by and see it for yourself!",
