    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal power delivery. Critical maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring structural and valvetrain integrity. The chassis remains communicative with refreshed bushings and balanced weight distribution, offering the tactile feedback synonymous with the platform. A mechanically sorted, driver-spec machine ready for the tarmac.",
