    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been such a reliable companion for all my trips. It runs great, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner. I've taken good care of it, and it's ready to hit the road today! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank, this is the one. Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
